OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FThere is no doubt that crime and
OL,8,Fpunishment is part of the DNA of
OL,9,FSomerset's County Town. But that
OL,10,Fhistory has a gap at the moment. Shire
OL,11,FHall, which is home to Taunton Crown
OL,12,FCourt, has been closed for nearly two
OL,13,Fyears and will remain that way until
OL,14,Fat least July 2026.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
