OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FRepairs to windows, roofing and
OL,8,Fessential stonework was needed to stop
OL,9,Fwater getting into the Grade Two-
OL,10,Flisted building. However, whilst
OL,11,Fcarrying out that work, the contractor
OL,12,Ffound a serious structural issues with
OL,13,Fthe flooring, which led to a complete
OL,14,Fclosure in September 2023. Planning
OL,15,Fpermission delays, as well as health
OL,16,Fand safety concerns, haven't helped to
OL,17,Fget it finished on time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
