OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FMy investigation into the works has
OL,8,Frevealed costs have spiralled by
OL,9,Fmillions of pounds - the total cost of
OL,10,Frepair work is now projected to reach
OL,11,Fnearly #12 million before VAT.
OL,13,FOne legal firm in the town says it's
OL,14,Fhaving a huge impact on victims,
OL,15,Ffamilies and businesses, with many
OL,16,Fcases having to be heard miles away.
OL,17,FTaunton's MP has labelled the
OL,18,Fsituation as 'scandalous'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
