OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FShire Hall is a beautiful building,
OL,8,Fbut is a sorry sight at the moment.
OL,9,FVandalism during the early stages of
OL,10,Fthe refurbishment work led to a
OL,11,Fperimeter wall being put up, locking
OL,12,Fthe old court site into custody for
OL,13,Fits own protection.
