OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FWhen I submitted my Freedom of
OL,8,FInformation Request, I expected to see
OL,9,Flarge figures money-wise, but to learn
OL,10,Fthat the costs are projected to almost
OL,11,Fdouble from the original contracts was
OL,12,Fa nasty surprise. With the project
OL,13,Fsplit into two phases, the original
OL,14,Fcontract costs totalled just under #7
OL,15,Fmillion before VAT. The projected cost
OL,16,Ffor all elements of the works now is
OL,17,Fstanding at just under #12 million
OL,18,Fbefore VAT. This is subject to change,
OL,19,Fbut indicates just how complicated and
OL,20,Fchallenging the work has been.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
