OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FIt was hoped that the site would be
OL,8,Fcompleted in January 2026 but the
OL,9,Fcurrent estimate for completion is
OL,10,FJune 2026, with the court becoming
OL,11,Foperational a month later.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/19
