OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FThe issue with this isn't that the
OL,8,Fwork is not important - it is. The
OL,9,FMinistry of Justice told me that, once
OL,10,Fcomplete, it will "improve the
OL,11,Fexperience of coming to court for
OL,12,Flocal communities, offering more
OL,13,Faccessible facilities and improving
OL,14,Fthe resilience of the building for the
OL,15,Ffuture". However, the time it has
OL,16,Ftaken for the work to be completed and
OL,17,Fthe cost to the taxpayer has caused
OL,18,Ffrustration, anger and concern locally.
