OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FSolicitor Lauren Preedy works for
OL,8,Flegal firm Amicus Law, which has an
OL,9,Foffice in Taunton. She says there has
OL,10,Fbeen a big impact on a lot of people,
OL,11,Fsaying: "You've got vulnerable people
OL,12,Fin our communities that are going
OL,13,Fthrough really difficult cases with
OL,14,Fchildren and if there is a delay in
OL,15,Ftheir court cases, then they could be
OL,16,Fleft in some really vulnerable
OL,17,Fpositions and some quite dangerous
OL,18,Fpositions as well."
OL,26,@sD@IOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
