OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FShe went on to say that cases are
OL,8,Fbeing moved to courts often a long
OL,9,Fdistance from Taunton. She said: "It
OL,10,Fcould be moved to Worle, which is on
OL,11,Fthe outskirts of Weston-super-Mare, or
OL,12,Fit could be moved to Yeovil or it
OL,13,Fcould be moved to Exeter. If they
OL,14,Fdon't drive, it's very difficult to
OL,15,Fget to some of these courts."
OL,26,@qD@bOUwD@]O]
