OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FLauren Preedy also said the closure,
OL,8,Fwhich has contributed to an already
OL,9,Fchallenging backlog in the justice
OL,10,Fsystem, has led to a time even more
OL,11,Fdifficult than during the Covid
OL,12,Fpandemic. She said: "If you compare
OL,13,Fthat to the court shutting, actually
OL,14,Fthe court shutting is probably the
OL,15,Fworst thing that I've known happen
OL,16,Fwith delays and the stress and the
OL,17,Fcost impact on people."
OL,26,@tD@UOUyD@WO]
