OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FClient services team leader at Amicus
OL,8,FLaw, Lee Baker, says the closure may
OL,9,Fbe contributing to an impact on the
OL,10,Fhousing market in the town as well,
OL,11,Fsaying: "What we're finding,
OL,12,Fparticularly (with divorces) where
OL,13,Fwe've got cases adjourned or cases
OL,14,Fsuspended and they've been delayed and
OL,15,Fpushed on three, six, nine months,
OL,16,Fwe're finding that houses can't sell."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, the town's current MP,
OL,19,FGideon Amos, says the delays and costs
OL,20,Fare "frankly scandalous" with the
OL,21,Fbuilding being "allowed to crumble".
OL,26,@sD@IOUxD@fO]|D@EOU|D@XO]}D@POU}D@cO]
