OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FHe said: "We need to get Taunton's
OL,8,FCrown Court back. Taunton should not
OL,9,Fbe ignored anymore, and I'm determined
OL,10,Fto make sure that is no longer the
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,F"We need to get this court back in
OL,14,Faction for the victims of justice, who
OL,15,Fare having to travel all the way
OL,16,Facross Somerset now instead, often
OL,17,Fwhen there's no public transport, and
OL,18,Ffor the whole local economy of Taunton
OL,19,Fand Somerset.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
