OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,F"I've raised it in the House of
OL,8,FCommons. I've met twice with the
OL,9,FJustice Minister. I'm determined this
OL,10,Fproject gets back on track and Taunton
OL,11,Fgets its Crown Court back."
OL,13,FThe maintenance and works at Shire
OL,14,FHall have been delivered in two
OL,15,Fphases. Phase one was all about
OL,16,Frepairs and improvements to windows,
OL,17,Froofing and stonework.
OL,26,@sD@[O]
