OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Justice said this
OL,8,Fbegan in February 2022 and was
OL,9,Fcompleted on schedule in October 2024.
OL,10,FThe original cost for this was nearly
OL,11,F#1.9 million, excluding VAT.
OL,13,FHowever, the FOI response shows that
OL,14,Fthe actual costs were much higher,
OL,15,Fbecause of additional costs including
OL,16,Fsecurity (caused by site vandalism).
OL,17,FThe total cost for the first phase
OL,18,Fended up being just over #6.9 million,
OL,19,Fbefore VAT.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
