OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FThe second phase, which includes key
OL,8,Finternal work, is set to be just over
OL,9,F#4 million, bringing the total
OL,10,Fprojected cost of the project to #11.9
OL,11,Fmillion before VAT is added. The costs
OL,12,Fof both projects are funded from the
OL,13,FMinistry of Justice and HM Courts and
OL,14,FTribunals Service budgets.
OL,16,FThe Ministry of Justice told me: "The
OL,17,Finvestment we are making demonstrates
OL,18,Four commitment to the building and
OL,19,Fretaining this vital public service to
OL,20,FSomerset."
OL,26,@xD@bOU|D@JO]
