OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FA spokesperson from HM Courts and
OL,8,FTribunals Service said: "Taunton Shire
OL,9,FHall is undergoing complex and
OL,10,Fextensive renovations to offer more
OL,11,Faccessible facilities for the local
OL,12,Fcommunity and ensure the resilience of
OL,13,Fthe building for the future. While
OL,14,FShire Hall is closed, Crown Court
OL,15,Fcases will be sitting at North
OL,16,FSomerset Courthouse in Worle, to keep
OL,17,Fcases progressing in the region."
OL,26,@pD@YOU
