OL,3,C'A scandal': The impact of Taunton
OL,4,CCrown Court closure - as repair costs
OL,5,Cspiral
OL,7,FFor all its architectural beauty and
OL,8,Fproud history, Shire Hall has become a
OL,9,Fsymbol of stalled justice in Somerset.
OL,10,FEvery extra month behind fencing means
OL,11,Fvictims waiting longer for closure,
OL,12,Fwitnesses travelling miles to give
OL,13,Fevidence, and public money draining
OL,14,Faway on a project that's already
OL,15,Fmillions over its original estimates.
OL,16,FWhen the doors finally reopen, for
OL,17,Fmany in Taunton, the verdict will be
OL,18,Fon why it took so long, cost so much,
OL,19,Fand left the county town without its
OL,20,FCrown Court for nearly three years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/19
